Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别管那些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑吗 的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面也必须尽快设下结界 否则就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化猫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半刻前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 卖药的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是小姐的出阁之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药是卖不出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是卖药郎来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖药郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是卖药郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说加世 看看你磨蹭多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 马上就做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你当今天是什么日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来送东西的吗 有什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是来卖药的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可没那个闲工夫 因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是真央小姐出嫁到志和野家的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这跟我们这些佣人无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概再过半刻左右来迎接的就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹冈 把障子拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是夫人这样就不能通风了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 也就一会工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出嫁吗 那可太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里有最适合新嫁娘用的药...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 不过...让我看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人 快滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不是你这种人能进来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 加世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水的话就快进来喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 回去晚了小心腾山大人发火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用说的那么过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点出去 否则饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也忒严厉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 看到他就让人生气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 比起这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 知道 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这边是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这药卖给真央小姐还真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 对方的新郎呀 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那新娘子也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是因为对方承担了这个家的债务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到出发时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好侍奉公婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万要保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人伊颢大人虽然是个好人 就是不擅长理财
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水江夫人面前好象也抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊国大人嘛也是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你想怎么轮到弟弟伊行大人继承家道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 竟然给你说了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里子管家知道了怕又要发火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为回报 我让你看一样好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是老鼠罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 这里好象有很多捕鼠器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买只猫不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呀 听说是因为有人讨厌猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问过弥平才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候你竟然在这里闲聊消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在说捕老鼠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世 去取水来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到龟都太渴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主 真央小姐 特来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 要照顾自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 坂井家的盛衰就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候里子去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央 起身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问一句 讨厌猫的原因是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠是子孙繁荣的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真央有福气哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你是怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是杀手所为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 对方也不是刀所能杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人 从哪里进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是加 加世擅自...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行迹可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑吗 的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面也必须尽快设下结界 否则就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 已经没气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看与其找医生不如直接找和尚了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊 国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(是你 都是因为你)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(夫人 你冷静下来)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(伊国 伊国 伊国 都怪你 都是你...)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道吗 嘿 这样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都是你 都是因为你...)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动 要是象刚才那样逃跑的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我在里面贴上符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话还来的及用结界封起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 住口 我看你是打算借机逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把他绑紧一点如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙会使用很怪异的武术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂已经断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样最好 活该
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有检查他的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央小姐会不会是被下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 刚才才说是被砍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的行李呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样 但不是毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个盒子里是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这刀是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么卖药的人要带着刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了杀死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没教养的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水江大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么妖怪 真不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么暗器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么暗器 里面没有设机关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能拔开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是不到时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这刀只有在被杀妖怪的形.实.式合一时才能拔开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾吧 我是一个很无趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可饶恕 送他到番所去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情闹大的话 我们会比较被动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腾山大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是现在家里最重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水江夫人 水江夫人 水江夫人 水江夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快叫医生来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去请坪内先生来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥平最好还是别出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界不是很完整
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 千万不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说是水江夫人身体不适所以来请先生去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志和野家那边也派人去传个话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主 那个还不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了真央猝死 志和野家会怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志和野知道还好说 要是主君知道了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好办法就是说真央得了急病 争取一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧 腾山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏的话反而会适得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们的嘴是无论如何也堵不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情已经恶化到不得不隐瞒的时候了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不如此 你不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为当务之急不是去志和野家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是开诚公布地请求帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们早这么做的话 管他志和野家如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的企图 你就坦白说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是替家主担心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果腾山大人你说我有企图的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就请你说说看我有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手段我领教了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要点灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世 真央小姐那里的灯也点上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 尸体...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何 你不会是不想去吧 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来点灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田岛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 这些都是妖怪所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么胡话啊 怎么可能有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 很快就会抓住凶手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田岛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你听到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么呀 小田岛 你别吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥平还没回来吗 怎么要用这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也有他们的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边可是大事 就是有安排也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让多话的可是腾山你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 也太迟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田岛 你看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这栋房子里面是没有猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从佣人们发出的尖叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥平 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家和真央小姐在奉安车里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人待着很危险 最好和大伙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 装神弄鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 那家伙进不来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你搞什么鬼 看我来揭穿你的鬼把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情形暂时稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西啊 完全看不清踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦离开结界就会成为它的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界也不能保持太久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去早晚会支撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须杀死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 拔开除魔剑需要条件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把妖怪的形.真实.理指示给除魔剑才能拔开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就是妖怪的形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是只化猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪成形需要人类的因果和缘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 关于这众生.真实和理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续


